{"tid":512748,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人可以分完手無耐又有新既","createTime":"2017-12-28T21:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T05:59:21.000Z","uid":4998,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"068314d34c378ee0538a6bebe11100636fe58bfe","tid":512748,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T21:02:51.000Z","msg":"自問如果曾經試過好深愛一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話咁易放低就放得低<br />\n就算時間唔算拍得好耐<br />\n每當諗起呢個人曾經同你一齊經歷過好多野<br />\n去過好多唔同既地方 有個人每一日都同你講早晨晚安 有人去分享自己既感受睇法 <br />\n相愛係件好難事 你要係成億人口入面 搵一個你愛佢佢愛你既人 仲要呢個人會令你有種想認識既衝動 有心跳既感覺 如果有真心愛過 係唔會咁容易放得低所有既野 轉頭就同第二個一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次就算好似有機會既時候 都係到提醒住我失戀之後個種痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個人好似惡夢咁牽連住我既過去同回憶 好似再搵唔到另一個你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好怕交完自己成個心出去之後又會被人拋棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又得返我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗我真係好怕好怕再接觸到其他人<br />\n2017年就結束 我唯一一個願望就係希望可以忘記你放得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6033f34d33f668f78a6638ceba4db631bf54ab4c","tid":512748,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T21:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似我 對方已經有新歡"},{"pid":"226749197379fa07776aeefa83012815f902a844","tid":512748,"uid":12908,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"因為未分手之前已經鍾意左第二個"},{"pid":"e75c8ba2b6cab5a05fee63607176d91e41241f94","tid":512748,"uid":29489,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"因為拍緊拖果時 keep 住身邊有貨"},{"pid":"c3f56b7311b0e89f6b9debee5cb40111406b4061","tid":512748,"uid":46862,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"因為係我飛人<br />\n決定分手嗰陣通常已經忍到極限<br />\n分手係釋然多過痛苦"},{"pid":"7e5cf7d2e43a11b305be5c69b14e6810dfdb44e3","tid":512748,"uid":21202,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:39:36.000Z","msg":"因為事實就係咁<br />\n係你地唔願意面對現實<br />\n放唔低一個咁快有新歡嘅人<br />\n只可以話係蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15119f612dbb9eaee0f5eb998cc92d571f50c545","tid":512748,"uid":62702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6033f34d33f668f78a6638ceba4db631bf54ab4c","tid":512748,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T21:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似我 對方已經有新歡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"對方結埋婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4b50e14f7b449872c88aeaa2cebb038518bf34","tid":512748,"uid":13809,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"最快去忘記一個人既方法<br />\n就係搵第二個人去分散注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c6fd898c76a3497c6b432574f095284291fdda","tid":512748,"uid":56414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"因為佢地唔夠愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2669a66d703c8fb37f8fa7f6f1fd95329fd2e269","tid":512748,"uid":113830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"因為你太差 人地都走夾唔抖"},{"pid":"c194847ba11e62b8f4493f531ec7cfef2f6e32ca","tid":512748,"uid":43460,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:30:19.000Z","msg":"因為對方唔夠愛你<br />\n抽離得快"},{"pid":"e40607a9e30c07ad8b74ca4d1125ea256288166a","tid":512748,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"分手幾日佢有左第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh